ADDITIONAL NOTICE

PocketTone Archive Pro is an unofficial, original web instrument inspired by
the general look and feel of vintage pocket keyboards. It is not affiliated
with, endorsed by, or sponsored by any keyboard manufacturer. All models,
names, skins, demos and lesson data in this project are fictional or original.

No copyrighted audio samples are used. All sounds are generated procedurally
via the Web Audio API. All lesson melodies are either in the public domain or
original compositions created for this project.
